                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>360° PTZ Cameras:</strong> Pan-tilt-zoom cameras provide complete lot coverage - no blind spots for thieves to exploit
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>4K Night Vision:</strong> Crystal-clear video even in complete darkness - identify faces and read VINs at 100+ feet
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>Motion-Activated Alerts:</strong> Real-time notifications sent to management when unauthorized activity detected after hours
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>Two-Way Audio:</strong> Live voice warnings to deter trespassers before theft occurs
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-600 mr-3">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>LED Floodlights:</strong> Bright motion-activated lighting illuminates suspicious activity and deters criminals
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Dealership Business Benefits</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">💰</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>Insurance Premium Reductions:</strong> Many insurers offer 10-15% discounts for active surveillance systems
