              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">📊</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>Incident Documentation:</strong> HD video evidence for police reports, insurance claims, and legal protection
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">👥</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>Customer Safety Assurance:</strong> Visible security presence makes customers feel safe browsing your lot
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">🏆</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>Competitive Advantage:</strong> Market your dealership as the safest place to shop for vehicles in Tacoma
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">📱</span>
                <div>
