                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">🎯</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>Scalable Coverage:</strong> Protect main lot, service area, and customer parking with multiple trailer placement
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ROI Calculator for Auto Dealers -->
