              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between pb-2 border-b">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Insurance discount (est):</span>
                <span class="font-bold text-green-600">-$1,200</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between pt-3 text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold">NET MONTHLY COST:</span>
                <span class="font-bold text-green-600 text-xl">$6,800</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">ONE Prevented Theft = 10+ Months of Protection</h3>
          <p class="text-xl mb-2">Annual Investment: $81,600 (12 months)</p>
          <p class="text-xl mb-4">Value of Prevented Theft: $70,000+ per incident</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold bg-white text-blue-600 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">Break-Even After First Prevented Theft</p>
          <p class="text-sm mt-4 text-blue-100">Most dealers prevent 2-3 theft attempts per year with visible surveillance</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Comparison Table -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <ComparisonTable
          title="Security Options for Auto Dealerships"
          description="Compare mobile surveillance trailers to traditional security solutions"
          headers={["Mobile Trailers", "Security Guards", "Fixed Cameras"]}
